welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Pewaukee, a charming city known for its beautiful lake views and friendly community. We invite you to explore and experience all that Pewaukee has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lawrence J Timmerman Airport handles all commercial flights and passenger services.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Lawrence J Timmerman Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at General Mitchell International Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is primarily used by Southwest Airlines for their domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse D
terminals.description: Concourse D is used by Delta Airlines for their domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse E
terminals.description: Concourse E is used by United Airlines for their domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport by selecting the network name and agreeing to the terms and conditions.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at West Bend Airport is the primary hub for all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at West Bend Airport caters to VIP and private charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
